<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-87-0587 </DOCNO><TEXT>This dictionary comprises about 14,000 entries in each of the four languagescovering the following fields: Air, Water, Water quality, Sewage treatment,Coastal engineering, Pollution of the sea, Flora and fauna, Ecosystems,Waste, Working environment, living conditions, environmental conditions,environmental monitoring. The dictionary deals above all with the technologicalaspects of environmental protection, i.e., techniques, methods, equipment,machinery, plants and plant systems. Terms regarding the scientific,socioeconomic and politico-cultural aspects have also been included,though in less detail.</TEXT></DOC>